THIRD-PARTY SOFTWARE NOTICES AND INFORMATION

This project incorporates components from the projects listed below.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Blender
   License: GNU GPL v3
   Copyright: Blender Foundation
   Website: https://www.blender.org/

   Saikei Civil is a Blender extension/addon that extends the functionality
   of Blender for civil engineering applications.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2. IfcOpenShell
   License: GNU LGPL v3
   Copyright: IfcOpenShell contributors
   Website: http://ifcopenshell.org/

   Used for reading, writing, and manipulating IFC (Industry Foundation Classes)
   files in accordance with buildingSMART standards.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

3. BlenderBIM Add-on
   License: GNU GPL v3
   Copyright: Dion Moult and contributors
   Website: https://blenderbim.org/

   Saikei Civil is designed to work alongside Bonsai for complete BIM
   workflows and IFC file management.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

4. MapTiler Coordinates API
   Service: MapTiler Cloud
   Website: https://www.maptiler.com/

   Used for coordinate reference system (CRS) search functionality.
   Users must obtain their own API key from MapTiler.
   API key is stored locally in Blender user preferences.

